ences in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Sections 815 and 818, referred to in text, are sections 815 and 818 of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/125"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–125","children":[],"tail":". Section 815 amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t49/s44901"},"text":"section 44901 of Title 49","children":[],"tail":", Transportation. Section 818 amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s8311"},"text":"section 8311 of Title 7","children":[],"tail":", Agriculture, and "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t8/s1356"},"text":"section 1356 of Title 8","children":[],"tail":", Aliens and Nationality."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This subchapter, referred to in text, was in the original “this subtitle”, meaning subtitle B (§§ 811–819) of title VIII of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/125"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–125","children":[],"tail":", which is classified principally to this subchapter. For complete classification of subtitle B to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t19/s4301"},"text":"section 4301 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
